BriefDescription: Marked Start probe nop completed. Instruction AND R0,R0,R0
Store finish count. Includes speculative activity
Cycles during which the marked instruction is the oldest in the pipeline (NTF or NTC)
Finish stall because the NTF instruction was a tlbie waiting for response from L2
Threshold counter exceeded a value of 32

Stores completed from S2Q (2nd-level store queue).  This event includes regular stores, stcx and cache inhibited stores.  The following ops are excluded (pteupdate, snoop tlbie complete, store atomics, miso, load atomic payloads, tlbie, tlbsync, slbieg, isync, msgsnd, slbiag, cpabort, copy, tcheck, tend, stsync, dcbst, icbi, dcbf, hwsync, lwsync, ptesync, eieio, msgsync)
Demand LD - L2 Miss (not L2 hit)
